description=Adreno 650 GPU drivers from Retroid Pocket Mini (V@0764.0, Jan 2024). Replaces stock V@0655.0 (Jun 2022). Fixes Vulkan crashes and improves performance. Optional Mesa Turnip Vulkan 1.3 driver selectable at install time.
